(340, 1, '2020-07-03 10:09:37', '2020-07-03 10:09:37', '<p>[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We understand the importance of database administration and hence provide the best possible database monitoring and administration services to our clients. We provide you with on-demand DBA resources for continued project management.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">24x7x365 Monitoring Promises Long-Term Database Health</h2>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">DBCHEFS database monitoring services encourages your DBAs to focus on the things that really matter and alleviates them from the constant worry of potential database alerts.</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Datavail operates 24x7x365 database monitoring and support with on-shift DBAs – not just on-call rotation – supported by our delivery centers. Utilizing multiple remote database monitoring locations enables our team to cover the time zones in which our clients operate.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">By combining both onshore and offshore services, represented by a U.S.-based Primary DBA, our remote database coverage provides benefits of an on-staff Tier-3 DBA, plus those of our remote service during “off” hours.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Key Features of DBCHEFS Monitoring Services:</h3>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Proactive database monitoring</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Issue tracking</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Ticketing system</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Customized notifications</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Break/fix resolution</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Incident history</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Remediation and prevention</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Other Database Monitoring Benefits:</h3>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">More accurate and timely alerts</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Fewer duplicate alerts</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Faster processing and response</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Flexible configuration</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Detection of changes in database environments</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Collects only what’s important for best practices</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Reduces single-points-of-failure</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Additional Enhancements Include:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Faster and easier setup</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Customizable “notes to DBCHEFS” per server</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Maintains state of open incidents until resolved</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Removes alert dependency on single local server</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Utilizes lightweight independent server agents</li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Highly secure HTTPS protocol</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>', 'Administration & Monitoring', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '19-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-07-03 10:09:37', '2020-07-03 10:09:37', '', 19, 'http://localhost:8080/dbsolutions/2020/07/03/19-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(341, 1, '2020-07-03 10:13:39', '2020-07-03 10:13:39', '<p>[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<p>When you outsource database management solutions to us, you can be assured that we take care of the data security aspect in a very serious manner. We ensure that all your confidential data is kept safe from any external threats.</p>\r\n<p>Databases are often overlooked as a target attack point when it comes to data hacking as they provide a rich repository of information for those who perform these breached. Organizations thereby can have a large, negative financial impact on their business if the security aspect of database is compromised upon.</p>\r\n<p>A comprehensive database scanning solution for vulnerabilities that affect databases such as default accounts, default permissions on database objects such as tables, views, and stored procedures, buffer overflows and denial of service. Regularly auditing database servers helps security staff identify configuration issues and policy and compliance violations.</p>\r\n<p>DBCHEFS powerful <strong>database monitoring</strong> and scanning solution Provides activity monitoring and blocking, privileged user and multi-factor access control, data classification, transparent data encryption, consolidated auditing and reporting, secure configuration management, and data masking.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Provides wide range of database audits for security, configuration and operational vulnerabilities</li>\r\n<li>Provides with pre-defined policy report templates, making compliance reporting for internal and external auditors effective;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Use the results from the database scan to penetrate the operating system and finding </p>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>', 'Database Security Management', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '20-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-07-03 10:13:39', '2020-07-03 10:13:39', '', 20, 'http://localhost:8080/dbsolutions/2020/07/03/20-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
